title: 13 Kids Who Are Definitely Not Yours
text:
View this image ›
Twitter: @petegima ID: 10522558 2. A kid who doesn’t think Zach Galifinakis is funny? Definitely not mine. View this image ›
Twitter: @melisalw ID: 10523001 3. A kid that refuses to finish pizza. Whose kid are you? View this image ›
Twitter: @CoachMason86 ID: 10522631 4. A kid who doesn’t want rice kripsy treats? Totally not my son! View this image ›
Twitter: @evanbrownell ID: 10522654 5. A kid who takes history notes? He’s too intelligent to be mine. View this image ›
Twitter: @Trailpolish ID: 10522566 6. A kid who likes to clean? There’s no way this one is mine. View this image ›
issa_may22 / Via instagram.com ID: 10522680 7. A kid who wants prunes and not chocolate? Not my genes. View this image ›
Twitter: @livethetreplife ID: 10522722 8. A kid who doesn’t make good trades? I don’t even know whose kid this could be. View this image ›
Twitter: @FSUcinnamonroll ID: 10522732 9. A kid who dips french fries in milk? This kid (who isn’t mine) needs to stopped! View this image ›
ariel_anne / Via instagram.com ID: 10522765 10. A kid who loves broccoli this much? I’m utterly confused at whose child this could be. View this image ›
Twitter: @mamajka42 ID: 10522741 11. A kid who enjoys folding laundry? I would never be lucky enough to have a child like this. View this image ›
mantha__3 / Via instagram.com ID: 10522917 12. A kid who enjoys math in their spare time? That’s impressive, but it can’t be my kid. View this image ›
Twitter: @A_Hagebusch ID: 10522971 13. A kid who only enjoys the middle brownie? Oh… now this IS probably my kid. View this image ›
